## üìä Analysis & Reporting Questions

### Attack Analysis:
```
"Analyze my recent DDoS attacks and provide mitigation recommendations"

"Show me the top attacked subnets in the last 30 days"

"What are the most common attack vectors targeting my network?"

"Provide a report on DDoS attack trends"
```

### Cost Analysis:
```
"Calculate the cost of on-prem vs cloud mitigation for my traffic"

"Show me the ROI analysis for the DDoS mitigation system"

"What's the estimated monthly cost for cloud scrubbing?"
```

### Capacity Planning:
```
"What scrubbing capacity do I need for my network?"

"Show me capacity planning for the next 12 months"

"How do I calculate mitigation capacity requirements?"
```

